data.description: Gorgeous Victorian home in the beautiful town of Beecher.  This home has a perfect chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances for the chef in the family including a 6-burner VIKING range and walk in pantry.  This home has beautiful original details on the staircase and throughout the house.  The wood floors are in great shape and have the same added details.  Enjoy the brisk mornings with a cup of coffee on the big screened in porch, the perfect enclosed back yard with a firepit, huge two car garage, and a great 1st floor bathroom.  This house is perfect for the family life with a 2nd floor laundry room,  four bedrooms and a master bath and 1/2 bath all on the 2nd floor. Tons of room for storage or a work space in the full unfinished basement and the oversized garaged.  This cute-as-a-button house is a must see!  Schedule your viewing today.
